| 레이어 | 사용 기술 |
|--------|-----------|
| **Frontend** | **Next.js 15** (App Router) · **TypeScript** · **Tailwind CSS v4** · **shadcn/ui** |
| **State/Data** | **TanStack Query** · **Zustand** |
| **Edge Functions** | **Supabase** Edge Functions (TypeScript + Deno) |
| **DB** | Supabase **Postgres** + Row Level Security |
| **CI/CD** | **GitHub Actions** → Vercel(프런트) / `supabase functions deploy`(백) |
| **테스트** | Jest/Vitest(Unit) · Playwright(E2E) |
| **품질 도구** | ESLint · Prettier · Husky + lint-staged |

